   VERSION=( "1.4.3" )
  CATEGORY="network utility"
 ATTRIBUTE="console"
  HOMEPAGE="http://sntop.sourceforge.net"
       URL="$SOURCEFORGE_URL"
    SOURCE="sntop/sntop-$VERSION"
       OPT="fping:::support for fping"
       REQ="ncurses"
 FRESHMEAT="sntop"
DESC="Simple network top (sntop) is a curses-based console utility

Simple network top (sntop) is a curses-based console utility in the spirit of top that 
polls network hosts at a regular interval to determine their connectivity and displays 
the results in a pretty format. Advanced features are supported, such as automatic HTML 
generation of results, secure terminal mode, execution of an external file on connectivity 
changes, a daemon mode, and user/system configure files.
"
